CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Flash Newspicture Magazine, February 28, 1938, pg. unknown, reads: "Another gay group at the Synchronettes party in Pgh. Earl Ormes, Betty Dorsey, Alderman and Mrs. Harry Fitzgerald await that refreshing pause between dances. (Pgh. photos by Charles 'Teenie' Harris)."
TitMainTitle: Earl Ormes, Betty Dorsey, Alderman Harry Fitzgerald, and Mrs. Fitzgerald posed in Loendi Club for Synchronettes Club party
